<h1 class="accent4 font-weight-400">Join Our Team</h1>
</div>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="segment body-background"><div class="container"><div class="row content"><article class="col-md-9 col-sm-8 col-md-push-3 col-sm-push-4"><p>Ready to join the team that puts our clients first and designs IT solutions that meet our purpose, focus and core values? WorkSmart is waiting to hear from you!</p>
<h2>Technical Support Representative</h2>
<ul class="fa-ul">
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>Location: United States, North Carolina, Durham</li>
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>Creation date: 2015-05-08</li>
</ul>
<p>We're looking for a IT professional who will thrive supporting a variety corporate clients and their users.  This position is in our Durham-based support center, and will provide support to our clients remotely (over the phone or using various remote support tools).  You'll join a team of 8 other support center representatives in delivering outstanding support to our clients and users.</p>
<p>Mainly operating in Windows environments, most of our clients are small businesses with little or no IT expertise in-house. We're not just looking for the best technical skills, we're also looking for folks who interact well with users - whether they're administrative staff or the business owner. </p>
<h3>Requirements</h3>
<h4>We're looking for folks who have at least: </h4>
<ul class="fa-ul">
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>2 years supporting Windows servers, including Exchange & SQL </li>
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>3 years providing end-user support (OS, Office, Printing & Scanning, Mobile Devices, etc.)</li>
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>1 years managing network equipment (firewalls, routers, switches, etc.) </li>
</ul>
<h4>You'll also need: </h4>
<ul class="fa-ul">
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>excellent communication (written and oral) skills </li>
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>excellent documentation and record-keeping skills </li>
<li><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa fa-li accent"></i>the desire and ability to learn new technology </li>
</ul>
<h3>Benefits</h3>
<p>This is a full-time salaried position with excellent benefits.</p>
